    <item>
      <title>A quick trip to Bjelovar for the opening of VOJIN BAKIĆ: The Principle of Hope —...</title>
      <link>https://www.instagram.com/p/DUMGnt5jCvq/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/626481588_18551671591005505_75982747646576330_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpegr_e35_p1080x1080_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=109&amp;ig_cache_key=MzgyMjQ1ODMyNzEyNTQ3MzIwMA%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjE0NDB4MTkyMC5oZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=oMJ6Mm8Me34Q7kNvwFjpxfb&amp;_nc_oc=Adq_tgAPj8Tp8lLtD4HR66FXaBs-vW5uHWrDOwjDyC9CscYAt1v65fbTQrdXuftG5sc&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;se=-1&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=oqzYekLPWN3Y7kbSxPaBSg&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfyLhdwwxz2xGwb8peerY3Cs0ROpVFWKhcctvF_Lk7-i9w&amp;oe=69C8F1B9" alt="Instagram billede fra @cultureoflies" /></p><p><strong>@cultureoflies</strong></p><p>A quick trip to Bjelovar for the opening of VOJIN BAKIĆ: The Principle of Hope — a timely and beautifully curated exhibition by Hana Ćurak @svesutovjeshtice at the Bjelovar City Museum @gradskimuzejbjelovar , marking the 110th anniversary of the sculptor’s birth. The first major showcase of Bakić’s work in his hometown in over 60 years.<br/>
<br/>
Thank you to @whw_what.how.for.whom for the recommendation, and to @ninakurtela for taking me to Dotrščina Memorial Park just outside Zagreb, where several of Bakić’s powerful works are set within the landscape.</p>]]></description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/626481588_18551671591005505_75982747646576330_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpegr_e35_p1080x1080_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=109&amp;ig_cache_key=MzgyMjQ1ODMyNzEyNTQ3MzIwMA%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjE0NDB4MTkyMC5oZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=oMJ6Mm8Me34Q7kNvwFjpxfb&amp;_nc_oc=Adq_tgAPj8Tp8lLtD4HR66FXaBs-vW5uHWrDOwjDyC9CscYAt1v65fbTQrdXuftG5sc&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;se=-1&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=oqzYekLPWN3Y7kbSxPaBSg&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfyLhdwwxz2xGwb8peerY3Cs0ROpVFWKhcctvF_Lk7-i9w&amp;oe=69C8F1B9" alt="Instagram billede fra @cultureoflies" /></p><p><strong>@cultureoflies</strong></p><p>A quick trip to Bjelovar for the opening of VOJIN BAKIĆ: The Principle of Hope — a timely and beautifully curated exhibition by Hana Ćurak @svesutovjeshtice at the Bjelovar City Museum @gradskimuzejbjelovar , marking the 110th anniversary of the sculptor’s birth. The first major showcase of Bakić’s work in his hometown in over 60 years.<br/>
<br/>
Thank you to @whw_what.how.for.whom for the recommendation, and to @ninakurtela for taking me to Dotrščina Memorial Park just outside Zagreb, where several of Bakić’s powerful works are set within the landscape.</p>]]></content:encoded>
